{"tid":2219303,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"抗暴之戰—4人被控襲警2人脫罪　官：警使用不合比例武力","createTime":"2020-09-26T18:40:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T18:40:17.000Z","uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"dc645f58c3feb8206051f8721bd37f8fffec11dc","tid":2219303,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T18:40:17.000Z","msg":"網民今年元旦日發起遊行，遭警方腰斬，晚上示威者轉戰旺角堵路示威，其間有便衣警遇襲，警方事後拘捕四名青年並控以襲警罪。裁判官林子勤昨裁決，裁定兩名把風者罪成，另兩人罪脫。林官更指警員證供誇大，其中一人僅路經現場，<span class=\"red\">被捕後即使表現合作，雙膝跪地，沒有掙扎，仍遭警方施以不合比例的武力，打至左面頰比右面大一倍，身體多處有瘀傷，結膜下出血。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I3jSo_cyxl4&amp;ab_channel=%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%8B%95%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9EHKAppleDaily\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DI3jSo_cyxl4%26ab_channel%3D%25E8%2598%258B%25E6%259E%259C%25E5%258B%2595%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259EHKAppleDaily&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0hURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=9ed78089\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I3jSo_cyxl4&amp;ab_channel=%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%8B%95%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9EHKAppleDaily</a>"}]}